CHANNEL_TABLE - Static variable in class de.acdgruppe.m2uhf_library.Enums
List with all channels for each Enums.Regulatory_Region The order of the regions is the same as Enums.Regulatory_Region So use the CHANNEL_TABLE.get(index) function with Enum.ordinal() as index to get the channels from a region
This list is read only, methods that modify contents will throw exceptions
